Wracked by insomnia and wanderlust, Kou Yamori is driven onto the moonlit streets every night in an aimless search for something he cant seem to name. His nightly ritual is marked by purposeless introspection until he meets Nazuna, who might just be a vampire! Kous new companion could offer him dark gifts and a vampires immortality. But there are conditions that must be met before Kou can sink his teeth into vampirism, and hell have to discover just how far hes willing to go to satisfy his desires before he can heed the Call of the Night!
(Source: Sentai Filmworks)

How can you fall in love when you cant even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will diewhich makes his flirty maids behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?
(Source: Funimation)

Daniel is an unattractive loner who wakes up in a different body. Now tall, handsome, and cooler than ever in his new form, Daniel aims to achieve everything he couldn't before. How far will he go to keep his body... and his secrets? (Source: WEBTOONS)

A hitman and a marriage swindler set out on the worlds most grueling battle for marriage! Gero is a young man from a clan of hitmen, which has been in existence for hundreds of years. As someone whos never gone to school and lived his life dealing in the dark side of the business, he considers himself to have no prospects with women and marriage as something not for him. However, one day, in fear that their lineage would dissolve, his clan warns Gero that if he doesnt marry and produce an heir, they would have no choice but toforce his little sister into doing that.
